  "body_html": "<p data-start=\"27\" data-end=\"124\">A collection of our most-loved perfumes over the past year — the scents you keep coming back for.</p>\n<p data-start=\"126\" data-end=\"228\">🤍 <strong data-start=\"129\" data-end=\"146\">Fluffy Mallow</strong> — a dreamy blend of citrus and sweet marshmallow, fluffy, playful, and addictive.</p>\n<p data-start=\"230\" data-end=\"333\">🍦 <strong data-start=\"233\" data-end=\"243\">Sundae</strong> — a warm vanilla gourmand with delicious sweet notes that make it impossible not to love.</p>\n<p data-start=\"335\" data-end=\"440\">✨ <strong data-start=\"337\" data-end=\"349\">Classy V</strong> — a sophisticated vanilla-amber scent that feels elegant, feminine, and effortlessly chic.</p>\n<p data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"585\">💍 <strong data-start=\"445\" data-end=\"454\">Wifey</strong> — the ultimate crowd favorite. Chic, feminine, and perfect for special occasions while still being light enough for summer events.</p>\n<p data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"677\"><strong data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"607\">Bundle includes:</strong><br>• Fluffy Mallow 50ml<br data-start=\"628\" data-end=\"631\">• Sundae 50ml<br data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"647\">• Classy V 50ml<br data-start=\"662\" data-end=\"665\">• Wifey 50ml</p>\n<p data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"766\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">The perfect bundle if you want to discover the scents that made Sorella a favorite. 🤍✨</p>",
